{"tid":2372043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平的口罩顯示什麼？","createTime":"2021-01-19T10:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T10:48:49.000Z","uid":261647,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24134054d80986f86c607c391a36f7b2fce9d4f1","tid":2372043,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:28:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/photos/a.454006908007166/4921408071267005/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fphotos%2Fa.454006908007166%2F4921408071267005%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmehAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=aaa077d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/photos/a.454006908007166/4921408071267005/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GU5Q5u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GU5Q5u.jpg&h=707ef002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【習近平的口罩顯示什麼？】<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平近日在北京考察冬季奧運會的籌辦工作。現場照片所見，無論是在室內還是室外，和官員一起還是和群眾一起，習近平幾乎在所有場合都把口罩戴得嚴嚴實實，同場人士亦然。<br />\n<br />\n然而翻看他兩個月前考察江蘇的照片，大部分時間都沒有戴口罩。而他三個月前考察潮州時，更是不戴口罩和大街上的大批群眾互動。<br />\n<br />\n有評論認為，要了解中國疫情的真實情況，與其相信官方數據，倒不如觀察習近平的口罩。你認為呢？<br />\n<br />\n#習近平<br />\n#口罩戴得嚴嚴實實<br />\n#疫情形勢吃緊"},{"pid":"6b333cab974e102e179c138391e489911e58f951","tid":2372043,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"p圖囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79ab449aba356dc9ac8357850044533d073db36","tid":2372043,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"戴口罩冇咁凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5ac5d4c56f98f55c20cf4b25ecbe127f17dc45","tid":2372043,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全国清零 不用戴口罩"},{"pi